&lt;li&gt;Own and continuously elevate ShopMy’s &lt;strong&gt;data foundation&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring data is reliable, scalable, and easy to use&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and maintain &lt;strong&gt;data models and pipelines&lt;/strong&gt; in Snowflake&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement &lt;strong&gt;monitoring, alerting, and validation systems&lt;/strong&gt; to proactively identify data and product issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Audit and improve data quality across sources, tracking, and transformations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve &lt;strong&gt;data usability and accessibility&lt;/strong&gt; across the business and support BI on a strong foundation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct analyses to identify and quantify opportunities to improve product performance and drive business impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product and Engineering on tracking strategy, feature development, and product performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in Data &amp;amp; Analytics with relevant industry experience (E-commerce, SaaS, Agencies, Social, or similar)&lt;/li&gt;
