&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a Senior Product Builder to focus on the Brand experience at ShopMy. You&#39;ll be the second Product Builder on the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Brand side of ShopMy is where revenue is generated and partnerships come to life. Brands use ShopMy to discover creators, manage gifting programs, run paid collaborations, track attribution, and measure ROI across their creator marketing spend. Your job is to make the brand experience so powerful and intuitive that ShopMy becomes indispensable to every brand&#39;s creator marketing strategy. You&#39;ll own surfaces of the brand-facing product, such as: discovery and search, gifting workflows, campaign management, analytics and reporting, and the daily tools that help brand teams operate at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a role where you write requirements and hand them off. You will take unclear signals - from brand feedback, sales conversations, usage data, and the market - and turn them into concrete product ideas. Then you will see those ideas through until they are live in production and changing real behavior.&lt;/p&gt;
